quote:
Tipuana Tipu
We launch FENLES Sound, a series of acoustic concerts where the music truly sounds live, up close, like you’ve never experienced before.
To kick off this madness, Tipuana Tipu joins us in a very exclusive format, one that only a few will be able to tell about.
Tickets are super limited and all proceeds will go directly to the artist to keep supporting their music.
If you love intimate concerts, the tiny desk vibe, and supporting those who are breaking the mold, this is your place.
Hurry, because by the time you hear how amazing it was, it’ll be too late.
Top vibe and flawless organization. Halloween done right.
